<i>adverb</i>: 정교히 [정교히], 은은히 [으는히], 은근히 [은근히], 오밀조밀 [오밀조밀], 야들야들 [야들랴들/야드랴들], 미묘히 [미묘히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정교히 [정교히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. delicately; elaborately</dd><br>
<dd>솜씨나 기술이 빈틈이 없이 자세하고 뛰어나게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being flawless, detailed and superb in skills or technique.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sophisticatedly; in meticulous detail</dd><br>
<dd>내용이나 구성이 정확하고 자세하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being precise and detailed in content or organization.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>은은히 [으는히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. indistinctly; delicately; dimly</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 보이는 무엇이 뚜렷하게 드러나지 않고 희미하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being vague, not appearing clearly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. dimly; distantly; faintly</dd><br>
<dd>소리가 들릴 듯 말 듯 약하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a sound being so weak as to be barely heard.</dd><br>
<dd>3. faintly</dd><br>
<dd>냄새나 맛이 진하거나 세지 않고 약하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a smell, flavor, etc., being moderate, not strong.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>은근히 [은근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. constantly and slowly</dd><br>
<dd>야단스럽지 않고 꾸준하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Steadily but not too strongly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tastefully; delicately</dd><br>
<dd>정취가 그윽하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Exquisitely.</dd><br>
<dd>3. quietly; secretly</dd><br>
<dd>행동 등이 드러나지 않고 은밀하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of behaving secretly so that others do not notice.</dd><br>
<dd>4. inwardly</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 나타내지는 않지만 속으로 생각하는 정도가 깊고 간절하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of thinking about something deeply and sincerely even though one does not reveal it.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오밀조밀 [오밀조밀]</dt><br>
<dd>1. elaborately; delicately; exquisitely</dd><br>
<dd>꾸미거나 정리하는 것이 매우 꼼꼼하고 정교한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very delicate and sophisticated manner in decorating or arranging something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. scrupulously; meticulously</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 태도가 매우 꼼꼼하고 자상한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one behaving with a very generous and careful attitude.</dd><br>
<dd>3. densely</dd><br>
<dd>물건이나 건물 등이 빈틈없이 모여 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of things, buildings, etc., standing close together.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>야들야들 [야들랴들/야드랴들]</dt><br>
<dd>1. softly; delicately</dd><br>
<dd>반들반들 윤기가 돌고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being glossy and smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>2. softly</dd><br>
<dd>목소리 등이 맑고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's voice, etc., being clear and tender.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>미묘히 [미묘히]</dt><br>
<dd>subtly; delicately</dd><br>
<dd>뚜렷하고 분명하지 않고 콕 집어낼 수 없을 정도로 이상하고 신기하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Unclearly, strangely and amazingly in a way that cannot be described.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>